  "content": "<p><strong>Etsy Picks: My Birthday Wish List! </strong></p>\n<p>This edition of <em>‘My Etsy Picks’</em> is quite special- it’s my birthday wish list! I thought about all the things I want for my birthday this year (which is in less than a week!!) and searched Etsy for them. I found a ton of beautiful items and wish I could have included them all, but these are the ones that made the cut!</p>\n<p>See the <a title=\"My Birthday Wish List Treasury on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTAzNjM3NjF8MjcyNjk4OTEwOA/my-birthday-wish-list\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>original treasury right here</em></a>, and check out all the talented artists below! My favorite things include crafting, cats, the warm and cozy and the simply lovely. That’s why I absolutely adore each of these items! I hope you do too! Be sure to fave their shops so you don’t miss out on their new items.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Mary John on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/186290957/solid-14k-gold-delicate-gemstone-stack?ref=tre-2726989108-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mary John</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Nothing But String on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/199358080/knit-fingerless-gloves-knit-gloves-grey?ref=tre-2726989108-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Nothing But String</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Simka Sol on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/115701331/wild-catalope-leggings-womens-black?ref=tre-2726989108-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Simka Sol</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Brandi Fitzgerald on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/187495669/love-park-reading-railroad-landmark?ref=tre-2726989108-4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Brandi Fitzgerald</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Marcellamoda on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/163376472/belted-open-long-cardigan-sweater-dress?ref=tre-2726989108-5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Marcellamoda</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"The Dreamy Giraffe on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/167357212/crafty-girl-typographic-print-craft-room?ref=tre-2726989108-6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Dreamy Giraffe</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Knit Fashionable on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/205942007/womens-sweater-knit-sweater-green?ref=tre-2726989108-7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Knit Fashionable</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Handcrafted Gifts on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/103560711/handspun-yarn-rainbow-merino-yarn-dk-1oz?ref=tre-2726989108-8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Handcrafted Gifts</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Silly Rice on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/176677530/strawberry-porcelain-ceramic?ref=tre-2726989108-9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Silly Rice</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"The Leather Store on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/192277304/tan-leather-bag-tan-leather-handbag?ref=tre-2726989108-10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Leather Store</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Simplicity Cosmetics on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/183916703/on-sale-mineral-eyeshadow-set-neutral?ref=tre-2726989108-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Simplicity Cosmetics</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"The Bold Banana on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/111031416/womens-cat-t-shirt-heart-sunglasses?ref=tre-2726989108-12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Bold Banana</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Jill Nicole Co on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/177222765/women-leggings-flower-leggings-colorful?ref=tre-2726989108-13\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Jill Nicole Co</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Decalgalor on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/202169520/halloween-black-cat-nail-art-water?ref=tre-2726989108-14\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Decalgalor</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Free Bird Cloth on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/180693908/womens-stripe-bow-sweater-long-sleeve?ref=tre-2726989108-15\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Free Bird Cloth</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Yarn Island on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/173272673/knit-scarf-unisex-scarves-cowl-scarf?ref=tre-2726989108-16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Yarn Island</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>What do you think of my birthday wish list? Which item is your fave?</p>\n",
